<name>Goopg</name>
<summary>GPG for Chromium GMail</summary>
<description>
<p>Goopg is a Chromium Native Messaging Host utility for GMail. it allows one
to verify and sign emails in a GMail web page, using GnuPG. The Chrome 'goopg'
Extension is also required.</p>
</description>
